Japanese(ja): 滞納中 - 早急にお支払いください
まだレビューはありません

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Absolutely perfect! The staff was so gentle and professional. My skin is silky smooth now. Will definitely come back!
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 完美无瑕！员工非常温柔专业。我的皮肤现在光滑如丝。一定会再来！
English(en): Absolutely perfect! The staff was so gentle and professional. My skin is silky smooth now. Will definitely come back!
Japanese(ja): 完璧です！スタッフさんがとても優しくて丁寧でした。お肌がツルツルになりました。絶対また来ます！

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): I've tried many places but this one is the best. No pain at all and the results are incredible. Highly recommend!
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 我试过很多店，但这里是最好的。完全不痛，效果惊人。强烈推荐！
English(en): I've tried many places but this one is the best. No pain at all and the results are incredible. Highly recommend!
Japanese(ja): いろんなお店を試しましたが、ここが一番です。全く痛くなくて、効果も抜群。超おすすめ！

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Best decision ever. The new laser machine is magic! The cooling gel was so refreshing too.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 做出的最好决定。新的激光机器太神奇了！冷却凝胶也很舒服。
English(en): Best decision ever. The new laser machine is magic! The cooling gel was so refreshing too.
Japanese(ja): 最高の選択でした。新しいレーザーマシン最高！冷却ジェルも気持ちよかったです。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Great service overall. Just a tiny bit of discomfort but nothing major. Would recommend to friends.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 整体服务很好。只有一点点不适，但没什么大问题。会推荐给朋友。
English(en): Great service overall. Just a tiny bit of discomfort but nothing major. Would recommend to friends.
Japanese(ja): 全体的にとても良いサービスでした。少しだけ痛みがありましたが、問題なし。友達にもおすすめします。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): The treatment was effective and the staff was friendly. Could use a bit more cooling gel though.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 治疗很有效，员工很友好。不过冷却凝胶可以多用一点。
English(en): The treatment was effective and the staff was friendly. Could use a bit more cooling gel though.
Japanese(ja): 施術が効果的でスタッフも親切でした。冷却ジェルがもう少し欲しかったかな。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Reasonable price for the quality of service. A few areas needed a second pass but overall satisfied.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 服务质量对得起这个价格。有几个地方需要再做一次，但总体满意。
English(en): Reasonable price for the quality of service. A few areas needed a second pass but overall satisfied.
Japanese(ja): サービスの質に対して価格が妥当です。一部やり直しが必要でしたが、全体的に満足。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): The result is fine, but the waiting time was a bit long. Also, the cooling gel was too cold.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 结果还行，但等待时间有点长。而且冷却凝胶太冷了。
English(en): The result is fine, but the waiting time was a bit long. Also, the cooling gel was too cold.
Japanese(ja): 結果は普通です。待ち時間が長かったし、冷却ジェルが冷たすぎました。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Nothing special. Got the job done but I expected more for the price.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 没什么特别的。完成了任务，但期望更高一些。
English(en): Nothing special. Got the job done but I expected more for the price.
Japanese(ja): 特に何もなし。仕事はしてくれたけど、価格の割には期待外れ。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Some areas were missed and had to point them out. Staff was polite though.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 有些地方漏掉了，不得不指出来。不过员工很礼貌。
English(en): Some areas were missed and had to point them out. Staff was polite though.
Japanese(ja): いくつかの箇所が抜けていて指摘しました。スタッフは丁寧でしたが。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): The technician was rushing and missed several spots. Had to ask for a redo.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 技师太着急了，漏了好几个地方。不得不要求重做。
English(en): The technician was rushing and missed several spots. Had to ask for a redo.
Japanese(ja): 施術者が急いでいて、何箇所も抜けがありました。やり直しをお願いしました。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Expected better results for the price. Some redness remained after treatment.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 期望价格能换来更好的效果。治疗后还有一些红肿。
English(en): Expected better results for the price. Some redness remained after treatment.
Japanese(ja): この価格ならもっと良い結果を期待していました。施術後に赤みが残りました。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): The equipment seemed old and the treatment was uncomfortable. Won't be my first choice next time.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 设备看起来很旧，治疗过程不舒服。下次不会是我的首选。
English(en): The equipment seemed old and the treatment was uncomfortable. Won't be my first choice next time.
Japanese(ja): 機械が古そうで、施術が不快でした。次回は他を選びます。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): The technician was rough and it hurt more than expected. I still have some stubble left. Won't be coming back.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 技师很粗暴，比预期的更痛。还有一些残留的毛茬。不会再来了。
English(en): The technician was rough and it hurt more than expected. I still have some stubble left. Won't be coming back.
Japanese(ja): 施術者が乱暴で、思ったより痛かったです。まだ毛が残っています。もう来ません。

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Wasted my money and time. The staff was rude and the results were awful. Avoid this place!
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 浪费了我的钱和时间。员工很粗鲁，效果很差。别来这里！
English(en): Wasted my money and time. The staff was rude and the results were awful. Avoid this place!
Japanese(ja): お金と時間の無駄でした。スタッフは無礼で、結果も最悪。ここは避けて！

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-CN): Burned my skin and no apology. This place is dangerous. Filing a complaint.
Chinese (Traditional)(zh-TW): 烧伤了我的皮肤，连道歉都没有。这个地方很危险。要投诉。
English(en): Burned my skin and no apology. This place is dangerous. Filing a complaint.
Japanese(ja): 肌をやけどされて謝罪もなし。ここは危険です。苦情を出します。
